@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rdixjt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.sin(wp.abs(v2 + 0.53)))
    tmp = ((wp.exp(v2 + 0.62) + wp.exp(v2 + 0.50)) * 0.37)
    tmp = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.54 - v0 + 0.51) * (v2 + 0.13 - v2 + 0.10)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.sin((tmp + 0.82 - tmp + 0.11)))
    v2 = ((wp.abs(v1 + 0.11) / v2) / (wp.sin(v2 + 0.29) + 0.77))
    data[tid] = v0
